source:
TEXT_LUCKZE003_03437_SEQ_00 Quest Sync
Joanric is at wit's end.
target:
TEXT_LUCKZE003_03437_SEQ_00Règle spéciale:  synchronisation de quête
Joanric semble tracassé...

source: TEXT_LUCKZE003_03437_TODO_00<tab>Survey the designated locations and defeat any gremlins that appear.
target: TEXT_LUCKZE003_03437_TODO_00<tab>Observer les environs aux endroits indiqués et abattre les éventuels <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0DF223380302 /var>

source: TEXT_LUCKZE003_03437_JOANRIC_000_000<tab>Oh, good traveler, thank the gods you're here! You simply must help deliver us from our unending nightmare. I speak, of course, of those godsdamned gremlins who keep sneaking in to defile the graves behind our fort.
target: TEXT_LUCKZE003_03437_JOANRIC_000_000<tab>Ô voyageu<var 08 E905 ((se)) ((r)) /var><var 1D /var>! J'ai besoin de votre aide<var 1D /var>! Pourriez-vous nous débarrasser de gremlins qui saccagent les tombes qui se trouvent derrière le fort<var 1D /var>?

source: TEXT_LUCKZE003_03437_JOANRIC_000_001<tab>Time and again have I and my fellow guards chased them away, only to see them come back in hordes, cackling and sniggering all the way.
target: TEXT_LUCKZE003_03437_JOANRIC_000_001<tab>Nous les avons déjà chassés plusieurs fois, mais ils reviennent toujours...

source: TEXT_LUCKZE003_03437_JOANRIC_000_002<tab>As if that weren't bad enough, they continuously berate us with an array of vulgar aspersions that─rather surprisingly given their limited intellect─more often than not hit painfully close to home.
target: TEXT_LUCKZE003_03437_JOANRIC_000_002<tab>Et en plus, ils ont pour manie d'injurier ceux qui les approchent. Même les plus hardis de nos soldats reviennent parfois les larmes aux yeux, traumatisés...

source: TEXT_LUCKZE003_03437_JOANRIC_000_003<tab>Why, it's gotten so bad that I─er, one of our men that was definitely not me spent the night crying into his pillow after the last such attack!
target: TEXT_LUCKZE003_03437_JOANRIC_000_003<tab>Alors on cherche une personne avec les reins solides, comme vous, qui n'a pas peur du jugement de petites créatures poilues, pour aller leur donner une bonne leçon<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_LUCKZE003_03437_JOANRIC_100_003<tab>But I can tell <var 1A 02 /var>you're<var 1A 01 /var> not one to let their words wound you, am I right? Of course I am! So I beg of you: go forth to the graveyard and be the gremlin-smiting hero we need!
target: TEXT_LUCKZE003_03437_JOANRIC_100_003<tab>Est-ce que vous pourriez aller mater ces gremlins insolents<var 1D /var>? Ils nichent dans le cimetière qui se trouve au nord de Fort Jobb.

source: TEXT_LUCKZE003_03437_JOANRIC_000_004<tab>I can just hear those godsdamned gremlins out there, sniggering at me and telling me what I should do to my amaro! Make it stop...oh, good gods, make it stop!
target: TEXT_LUCKZE003_03437_JOANRIC_000_004<tab>Est-ce que vous pourriez aller mater ces gremlins insolents<var 1D /var>? Ils nichent dans le cimetière qui se trouve derrière le fort.

source: TEXT_LUCKZE003_03437_SYSTEM_000_010<tab>You can neither see nor hear any sign of gremlins here...
target: TEXT_LUCKZE003_03437_SYSTEM_000_010<tab>Il n'y a visiblement aucun <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 0DF223380202 /var> dans les environs... Mieux vaut chercher ailleurs.

source: TEXT_LUCKZE003_03437_BALLOON_000_000<tab>Lick the spittle from the floors, lickspittle!
target: TEXT_LUCKZE003_03437_BALLOON_000_000<tab>Hin hin hin<var 1D /var>! Va mourir la bouche ouverte<var 1D /var>!
TEXT_LUCKZE003_03437_BALLOON_000_010<tab>Laisse tomber<var 1D /var>! Tu sers à rien, de toute façon<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_LUCKZE003_03437_BALLOON_000_030<tab>Yer lower than piss on the privy!
target: TEXT_LUCKZE003_03437_BALLOON_000_030<tab>Tu ne le sais pas, mais tu es déjà mort<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var><var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_LUCKZE003_03437_BALLOON_000_040<tab>Is that sorry blow the best ye got?
target: TEXT_LUCKZE003_03437_BALLOON_000_040<tab>Pourquoi insister<var 1D /var>? Ça sert à rien... comme toi<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_LUCKZE003_03437_JOANRIC_000_020<tab>Do my ears deceive me? The tittering and snickering is no more... Could it be? Dare I dream? Have you put an end to the gremlin menace once and for all!? O, glorious─ Ahem. That is to say, thank you, traveler. All of Fort Jobb is in your debt!
target: TEXT_LUCKZE003_03437_JOANRIC_000_020<tab>Oh, vous avez donné une leçon aux gremlins<var 1D /var>? Formidable<var 1D /var>! Merci beaucoup<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_LUCKZE003_03437_JOANRIC_000_021<tab>...Forgive me, I get carried away when the topic turns to those nasty buggers. Speaking of which, do you ever wonder where they came from? I could swear I never saw one of them before the Flood.
target: TEXT_LUCKZE003_03437_JOANRIC_000_021<tab>Je me demande d'où viennent ces horreurs. On n'avait jamais vu de telles créatures avant le déluge de Lumière...

source: TEXT_LUCKZE003_03437_JOANRIC_000_022<tab>I heard someone saying that they first started popping up after the Crystarium was built. That they came out of the tower. As for the truth, who can say, but all I know is that they're not bothering us anymore, and that's good enough for me!
target: TEXT_LUCKZE003_03437_JOANRIC_000_022<tab>Certains pensent qu'ils viennent de la tour, parce qu'on a commencé à les voir depuis la fondation de Cristarium, mais bon... allez savoir. En tout cas, grâce à vous, le cimetière a enfin retrouvé sa tran<var 16 /var>quil<var 16 /var>li<var 16 /var>té<var 1D /var>!
